                                                             'Andy (Anne Hathaway) is a recent college graduate with big dreams. ' ||
                                                             'Upon landing a job at prestigious Runway magazine, she finds herself the assistant' ||
                                                             ' to diabolical editor Miranda Priestly (Meryl Streep). Andy questions her ability to ' ||
                                                             'survive her grim tour as Miranda''s whipping girl without getting scorched.',5.99,1,14);

